results.name: Lesser prime factor of n-th product of two distinct primes.
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
program: (PARI) go(x)=my(v=List()); forprime(p=2, sqrtint(x\1), forprime(q=p+1, x\p, listput(v, [p*q,p]))); apply(v->v[2], vecsort(Vec(v),1)) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Sep 14 2015
results.author: _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Jul 15 2004
